This is how to is_palindrome of text:
   Remember that n is text's length
   Remember that half is quotient of n and 2
   Remember that i is 0
   Do this half times:
      Remember that j is diff of (diff of n and 1) and i
      When item i in text is not item j in text, then:
         The answer is 0
      End when
      Increase i
   End do
   The answer is 1
